Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我緊緊地纏繞的話不行喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.56,0:22:49.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.82,0:22:55.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:23:08.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.02,0:23:19.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.77,0:23:27.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能  太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.15,0:23:33.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.57,0:23:44.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.57,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有很多警察先生出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團也一起做推理立功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.77,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑警戀愛物語2(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經有一點察覺到妳的真面目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.82,0:01:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼繼續隱藏下去也沒有意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.66,0:01:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會傷害她而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要告訴我這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.47,0:02:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠看透邪惡的你這雙正義之眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能明白女人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從第一次見面之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.46,0:02:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你並沒有發覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡！卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要表現得更加驚訝一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一幕是背叛黑道的女間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對假面超人告白的一個衝擊的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是學藝祭要表演的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣應該做些更加平常的戲劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如桃太郎或者是一休和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.68,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼荒謬的故事 我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人不是也差不多嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.01,0:02:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是委屈求全扮演大番薯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別那麼多牢騷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.67,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地為了讓大家感受到真正的現場環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地跑到廢棄大廈裡面來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣不如演警察故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種故事不是常常出現嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察進入廢棄大廈時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧遇見強盜的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起雙手 不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.09,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.52,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.58,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跑到頂樓去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 你從下面追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被已逮捕的犯人給脫逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要把他帶回總部的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了機車和卡車相撞事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.39,0:05:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人趁我不注意的時候偷偷地跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他看起來很老實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本沒想過他會逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.14,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真粗心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的被逃走的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去不是寫報告就可以了事的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18點43分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將逃亡中的犯人逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手銬的鏈子斷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要給人添麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是掉在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不要這麼莽撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有殺人 警察小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才上面是不是有什麼奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太多疑了吧？ 上面全都上鎖了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快把工作做完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是美術館嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼一幅畫也沒有呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是正在更換作品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.03,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說很危險要你們趕快回家去的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木 我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 這裡可是男廁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那個逃犯怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓是抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻出了點意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按常理手銬應該是銬在犯人的雙手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不想讓他再跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就銬到自己的手上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被一課的人知道的話會很丟臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以偷偷幫我拿備用鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能偷偷地呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為犯人逃走現在大家都很緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對前輩竟然講這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是你不小心看守讓犯人給逃掉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是這樣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜託你了 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過早上我醒來之後村西小姐就已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從剛才就一直這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 請相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 東田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是和你住在同一座公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你公司的上司村西真美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡現場是她的房間的浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當發現她死亡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正喝醉酒睡在她的床上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的門鎖也是用門鏈鎖上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以房間是個密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房間的鑰匙還有門鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有繞在死者脖子的三色電線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有你的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.73,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你在工作上常常和她起爭吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天你不是和她在酒吧裡面吵了一架嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們只能認為是你跑到她的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用電線殺了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鎖是為了不讓她逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在殺害她之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為喝醉所以就睡在她的床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一點印象都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說是因為你酒後殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確因為她在工作上常找我麻煩讓我很恨她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我卻沒有恨到要殺她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你為什麼要逃呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有個地方必須去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到加拿大的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我離婚後讓太太撫養的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要結婚的喜帖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為她這17年來一直恨著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我有理由不去參加嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到我的房間去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以看到我女兒寫給我的信和飛機票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大叔不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這位大叔放了步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是壞人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會這樣做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天幾點的飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田機場12點30分出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意照我的話去做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.43,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 聯絡不到佐藤和高木？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直打他們的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是追蹤犯人中發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找 他們二人應該還在那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥 我們也過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天12點前要找到真正犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我會好好看著他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這種樣子也無法行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去拿鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶回警署然後我們再…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果回警署拿鑰匙被發現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被上級罵到臭頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寫報告的時候 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機早就飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽著 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就假裝我們現在正在尋找逃走的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找出真正的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫌犯被移送檢察署之前 如果已經證明他的清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們警察就可以決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移送之前就直接釋放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後期限就是這間美術館開館的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上10點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有客人進入這個廁所的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候也會通知警方過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我願意相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就我一個人實在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不是一個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像很有幹勁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 最後期限是明天早上10點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前你要找出真正的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明他是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你一定辦得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信自己的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官的心上人不是目暮警官嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些話是為了讓我增加信心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從剛才就一下子興奮一下子失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樓梯下面不是有寫著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「禁止進入」的標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了緊急狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們大家在追犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼犯人 你們又不是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實我是警視廳的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 逃亡中的這個嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我警察的身份被發現的話行動就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他能趕得及參加她女兒的婚禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須秘密的自己去做調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在玩警察遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.92,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個警察好像很靠不住的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良又容易做錯事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種不能放心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在緊急時刻也會很努力去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.18,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也在身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個戴眼鏡的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子總是很令人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第5輛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事情了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說他們是在找犯人和我和佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木刑事好像殺手一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 要做秘密調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 首先要先調查那間店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.73,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東田先生在案發前最後去過的那間居酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得爛醉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今天一定要打死那個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想不到東田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的做了那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一個人回去的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和他一起喝酒的北川先生一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二個人一起走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和東田先生是同一個公司的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就是他了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個發現屍體的北川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個發現者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.45,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發隔日因為東田先生和村西小姐沒上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他拜託管理員幫忙開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就在那裡發現了屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我放在桌子上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是警察 有幾件事情想請問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說的我都已經向警察說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司被朋友給殺害 我也很受打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請暫時讓我自己冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 他已經在警局錄了口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.77,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的居酒屋老闆也被問過很多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 北川先生是東京Spirits的球迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東田先生是反東京Spirits的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們在問些什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打電話回家 媽媽會擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.91,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.03,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼可能在明天中午之前找到真正的犯人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說你們大家今天都要住在我這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們和高木警官一起我也很放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且明天是星期日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.98,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴他們你們在這裡討論該如何慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶祝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.91,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的發明終於可以貢獻社會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稱做熱帶彩虹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸時會有七色彩虹出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情做完了 記得過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士說可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.32,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是明天杯戶鎮會有個煙花大會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花 有這個慶祝節目嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 接下來就是案發現場村西小姐的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是警察啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.51,0:17:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午的警察先生們才剛走不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有一些東西沒有調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小孩子們呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來做生活實習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要看看警察先生的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後到學校去做發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～就像是「朝九晚五的叔叔」之類的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等一下會把鑰匙拿到管理室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要亂碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才高木刑事在買帽子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也買了這些手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯南叫我們買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.55,0:17:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯、佐藤跟高木他們到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們追嫌犯到杯戶鎮的廢棄大樓內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就失去聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官竟然幾個小時都沒有聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個人都落到了嫌犯手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然對我重要的部下出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 嫌犯將佐藤給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美和子被軟禁了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 感冒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因為我讓妳著涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的抓錯人該道歉的人應該是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.93,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不是為了你而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想讓你女兒和我有同樣不好的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候就失去父親的那種寂寞感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼找也找不到什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查人員進來的時候地板一點毛髮也沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的有四個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個是枕頭 棉被 床單還有窗簾的顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.64,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚房的廚具餐具還有裝潢全部都是米黃色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有床和窗簾是灰色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.19,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過米黃色的窗簾和床單都在衣櫃裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且居酒屋的老闆娘講過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村西小姐最喜歡米黃色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還喜歡東京Spirits跟仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後東田先生對視聽器材很詳細卻討厭洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉之後就會不省人事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常早上上班都會遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事在錄口供的時候都沒有講過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們認為警方錄口供的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講一些與事件無關的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能會被責備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以經常會只講重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.88,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別看她那樣子 那個老闆娘很八卦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個就是不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿掉的床邊的月曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這是在櫃子裡面拿出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京spirits這個月的月曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.39,0:20:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和後面的日曬痕跡剛好一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是因為最近球隊沒發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會把它拿下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月份的預定事務都寫在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三就是傢俱有被移動過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點調查的人員也講了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是傢俱更換吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在移動衣櫃的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.33,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒發覺到將這麼重要的東西掉到櫃子底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是一個普通的火柴盒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打開看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有一張紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村西小姐的結婚申請書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她是準備結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過男方的名字卻沒有寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面卻已經蓋了章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四是仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當日早上下了一些雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡仙人掌的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓仙人掌就這樣放在外面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 除了她之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰不知道為了什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將許多東西給移動過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當日的傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘送給她的禮物 圓球仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過上面的針葉斷掉了 真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這又能證明什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯的東田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.69,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天把這裡當作自己的房間睡在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是兇器的三色電線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的鎖 還有門鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有東田先生的…指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個房間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要不要去看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的房間也在這棟公寓裡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.88,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.14,0:23:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我們快點進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真正犯人的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.12,0:23:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的他說什麼來著？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是炸彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.24,0:24:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.30,0:24:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.10,0:24:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.28,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.27,0:24:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.32,0:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.39,0:24:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事戀愛物語2(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.24,0:24:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.77,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.43,0:24:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回刑事的戀愛有結果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.31,0:24:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是和目暮警官
